{"tid":2067413,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"田北俊稱成立「希望聯盟」冀回到自由黨成立時中間路線","createTime":"2020-06-17T03:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T12:52:27.000Z","uid":60281,"like":4,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"9eb08037edb15148f1a248809b1b386ac57908ad","tid":2067413,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:45:37.000Z","msg":"仲有中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自由黨榮譽主席田北俊表示，成立「希望聯盟」，是想回到93年自由黨成立時走中間路線的目標。被問到前財政司司長曾俊華的角色，田北俊表示，曾俊華支持他成立聯盟但不想積極參與，但會在行動上支持。至於會否招攬立法會前主席曾鈺成，田北俊表示，曾鈺成的中間路線看法與他們接近，但對方仍是民建聯成員，立場亦比他「藍」好多，相信未必能合作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532529-20200617.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532529-20200617.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXGyC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=b2e58c7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532529-20200617.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=838fd5e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532529-20200617.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"2da7d9fe2c2687985934ca22efba4817609b25c2","tid":2067413,"uid":185652,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:46:32.000Z","msg":"好傻好天真<br />\n仲信有一國兩制<br />\n港人治港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a6ca66c9fdae4710ce8b027fdb812913d76ab4","tid":2067413,"uid":54415,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:46:34.000Z","msg":"做咩唔入再恤髮，大把中立淺藍喎"},{"pid":"cbc612cf6320318d49353244bd7014a7d1dc8415","tid":2067413,"uid":83328,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:48:50.000Z","msg":"又嚟中間超人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hk01.com/medi